        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Can I rent a car without a credit card?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
          Most rentals require a credit card for security, but some locations accept debit cards with restrictions.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Is there a mileage limit on rentals?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
          Mileage limits depend on the rental agreement; some cars offer unlimited mileage.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
